Package ca.queensu.cs.cisc124.notes.generics.list

Interface SList<E>

  • Type Parameters:
    E - the type of elements in this list
    All Superinterfaces:
    Iterable<E>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    SArrayList, SLinkedList
    public interface SList<E>
extends Iterable<E>
    A simplified list interface. A list represents a finite collection of elements held in a linear sequence.
